252
00:17:20,870 --> 00:17:24,460
Another thing to do is to write
some questions down for yourself.

253
00:17:24,460 --> 00:17:26,820
You don't have to be an expert
on what you're writing about,

254
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:28,510
you just have to be clear.

255
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:30,280
Write down what puzzles you.

256
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:31,800
Write down what confuses you.

257
00:17:33,370 --> 00:17:35,540
I am confused about x.

258
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:38,530
I am puzzled about how x relates to y.

259
00:17:38,530 --> 00:17:45,560
Write these things down, cover several
pieces of paper with ideas and sketches.

