00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,360
It can even look like this.

261
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:50,730
Tape them together.

262
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:54,430
Cover a bunch of paper, with notes.

263
00:17:54,430 --> 00:17:55,210
Tape them together.

264
00:17:56,735 --> 00:18:00,090
Set them down on your desk and
go out for a half an hours walk.

265
00:18:00,090 --> 00:18:02,430
When you come back, start again.

266
00:18:02,430 --> 00:18:04,220
You will have more ideas.

