271
00:18:21,210 --> 00:18:26,100
In terms of readability,
I would suggest using short sentences.

272
00:18:26,100 --> 00:18:28,515
A writer ought to go into his paper, and

273
00:18:28,515 --> 00:18:31,500
if he has written any really
long sentences, ask himself,

274
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:36,930
